ground_truth:
If you are just adding it in the new version, you can use an augment decorator to version the property, as in this playground

```
/** A ContosoProviderHub resource */
model Employee is TrackedResource<EmployeeProperties> {
  ...ResourceNameParameter<Employee>;
  ...ManagedServiceIdentityProperty;
}

// here is the augment decorator for versioning
@@added(Employee.identity, Versions.`2025-10-01-preview`);

